cp510.assignments.geo_shape

Class GeoShape

  • java.lang.Object
    • cp510.assignments.geo_shape.GeoShape
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    GeoLine, GeoRectangle

    public abstract class GeoShape
extends java.lang.Object
    The GeoShape class for UW java 510 assignment 4 (GeoShape part 1). The GeoShape class determines the origin point of the generated shape. It contains x and y coordinates and the fill color for the shape. It also contains setters and getters for these two attributes. This class encapsulates functionality common to all shapes in the geo_shape package. It is also an abstract class.
    Author:
    Toby Peterson.
